  • Classes in com.qtplaf.library.app used by com.qtplaf.library.app 
    Class and Description
    AccessMode
    An access restriction to a menu option, action button, table columns or any defined string key.
    Argument
    Startup or command line argument to help the management, i.e. validation and reading in any order, of the main arguments.
    Security
    Generic security interface to map user access to string keys.
    Session
    A session manages the featurs related to one user executing one instance of the system.
    User
    A user of the system applications.
